
Python运行环境安装：



官方地址:  https://selenium-python.readthedocs.io/installation.html#drivers




firefox环境：

驱动下载： https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases/download/v0.24.0/geckodriver-v0.24.0-linux64.tar.gz

wget https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases/download/v0.24.0/geckodriver-v0.24.0-linux64.tar.gz
tar -zxf geckodriver-v0.24.0-linux64.tar.gz && mv geckodriver /usr/local/bin
pip3  install selenium requests   #提示版本问题就执行下面的指定站点安装即可
pip3 install sqlmap -i http://pypi.douban.com/simple/ --trusted-host pypi.douban.com

简单的爬虫环境!



火狐浏览器安装：
wget https://download-ssl.firefox.com.cn/releases/firefox/66.0/zh-CN/Firefox-latest-x86_64.tar.bz2
tar -xvjf Firefox-latest-x86_64.tar.bz2
mv firefox /usr/local/bin/



谷歌环境：

驱动下载： https://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/index.html?path=73.0.3683.68/


